*Oženio* se u zadnje vrijeme. (He got married recently.)

*Oženila* se nakon tri godine zajedničkog života. (She got married after three years of living together.)

Njegov otac se *oženio* kada je imao 25 godina. (His father got married when he was 25 years old.)

*Oženivši* se, on je napustio svoj rodni grad. (After getting married, he left his hometown.)

Njegov brat je *oženio* svoju dugogodišnju djevojku. (His brother married his long-time girlfriend.)